title: INCREDIBLE 3 BED 3 BATH IN BUSHWICK W/D IN UNIT AND GYM!!!! NO BROKERS FEE
posting_body: ['Call/Text Hindy (703-973-4218) for a showing TODAY!!', 'Huge 3 bed 3 bath available W private bathroom and W/D in unit in BEDSTUY!!', 'Each large room has a full bathroom with deep soak tub inside, large windows and spacious closets.', 'The living room kitchen area is complete with exposed brick, brand new stainless steel appliances and very high ceilings!', 'Make this apartment yours TODAY!!', 'FEATURES:', '-W/D in unit', '-Large spacious rooms with private bathrooms with deep soak tubs and closets', '-Modern finishes and exposed brick throughout', '-Full kitchen with dishwasher', '-Great natural light', '-High ceilings', '-Prime location', '-Pet friendly', '-Gym', '-Furnished roof deck', '-No fee', 'AREA:', 'Building is in thriving Bed-Stuy area, near supermarkets, yoga studios, Michelin star restaurants, really cool music venues and bars.', 'Near many public transit options, short commute to the city.', 'MUST HAVE GOOD CREDIT AND INCOME!', 'Guarantors WELCOME']
